{"tid":1391220,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新手去旅行 - 泰國, 自己買機book酒店定買pakage好？","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T21:36:26.000Z","uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bec7696498a769050cb84f7aeab7c7abf173083","tid":1391220,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"諗住自一丁友去泰國散心，咁大個仔都未試過自己去第個國家旅行。<br />\n各巴打有冇心得可以同預弟弟分享下？有幾條問題想問：<br />\n<br />\n1. 泰國安全嗎？有咩頭暈身興醫院會唔會收好貴同埋靠唔靠得住（小弟身體差）？<br />\n2. 買機票book酒店自己散買定買果D 永安旅遊5天4夜自由行套票好D抵D？<br />\n3. 泰國除左SPA 仲有咩好玩？<br />\n4. 5天你地會點plan行程法？<br />\n有更多既野可以隨便Share, 等其他有性趣去泰國既巴打都覺得有用。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事成會返黎Share&nbsp;我一丁友之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dae673381af43c6b14ca390d08e6c58fe117b8b","tid":1391220,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"泰國冇問題唔好幫襯永安係大陸公司"},{"pid":"ff4c7c2355f3e3ccfb40d46a1c75f54190836a6d","tid":1391220,"uid":22999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"泰國咁大你去曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e50ba3d1fddb814df90d59a16400cc744bda979","tid":1391220,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4c7c2355f3e3ccfb40d46a1c75f54190836a6d","tid":1391220,"uid":22999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"泰國咁大你去曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"曼谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal